        <Parent_String>woodworking vises [300024224], tools for wood-holding and -assembling [300024107], woodworking tools [300163324], woodworking equipment [300163322], equipment by material processed [300168082], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
